Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們邂逅於偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最初　我本對她一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但看到她在面前哭泣　我也會同樣悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看到她緊緊地抱住我　心中便隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看到她露出笑容　我也同樣欣悅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管不知該如何表達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但她是我無以替代的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這一次　我一定會堅守那未能兌現的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以　等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽一定會將妳救回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧　鋼鐵伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.60,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「沒問題」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.60,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kein Problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,奈葉應該已經到達王座大廳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.07,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Ja.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,疾風也在苦戰中等待這艘船停下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.53,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Richtig.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,必須破壞掉它　使這艘船停下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,限界昇華　能行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.47,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Jawohl.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.10,Faqi,,0,0,0,,　Zerstörungsform　{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}裂滅形態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H81111EE&)}裂滅旋槌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.83,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「檢測到危險的魔力反應」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.83,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eine magische Reaktion wurde ausfindig gemacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:04:03.55,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「啟動防衛模式　接近驅動爐者將遭受無差別攻擊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.90,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wir gehen in die Verteidigungssituation ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.22,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}　Alles, was sich dem Kern annährt,　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.55,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}　wird unbedingt {\fsp-12}zü{\fsp0}gig angegriffen.　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,距離次元航行部隊到達　還有45分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,距離巨舟到達軌道地點　還有38分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,7分鐘時間差…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它的主炮對準了米德首都
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,若是有7分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,足夠讓它發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,防衛線　維持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來接替一下指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也突入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不能讓它升入環球軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也絕不能讓它攻擊地面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,八神部隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是長弓3號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿露特？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,八神部隊長　請再稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我正將搭檔送往妳的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便叫我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.72,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}Chain Bind{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}束縛光鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,根本沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.11,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}Round Shield{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}魔力環盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:57.46,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「WAS區劃2結束　開始搜索區劃3　請再堅持一下」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:57.46,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}WAS, Area 2 complete. Beginning area 3.\NThis will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,星煌2級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.38,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Blaster 2nd{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}星煌2級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,旭煌伴星…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}水晶牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,封鎖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這招已經學會了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓那惡魔盡情強化自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,星煌系統的奧秘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是遠遠超出身體限界的自我強化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,越是去使用　越是去強化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,便越會吞噬使用者與魔導器的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,若能與優秀的前衛配合\N\N不必考慮任何後顧之憂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的確會是一擊必殺的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但這種情況下　是根本派不上用場的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道自己該做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,地雷王　不可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,牙龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,凱珞　妳帶著露到上空去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,地雷王們就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請隨我歸案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須營救露緹茜婭　並阻止斯卡列迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,斯卡列迪與戰鬥機人們已被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的部下們正設法營救\N\N露緹茜婭{\fnsimhei}·{\r}阿爾皮諾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　我也就只剩下最後一個使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥？　為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我全力追求著夢想中的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺間卻走上了完全不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「守護信念中的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,──這看似簡單　卻又是多麼困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H8963696&)}紫電一閃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是驅動爐那裡的小騎士…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼打不破
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,若不能毀掉它　大家都會有危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,疾風也好　奈葉也好\N\N我必須去守護她們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不將它砸碎　就全無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…　鋼鐵伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:39.74,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Jawohl!{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,粉碎吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒能守護大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,疾風…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,…疾風？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,…琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵槌騎士維塔與鋼鐵伯爵\N\N付出了如此的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在這世界上　難道還有什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,──會無法粉碎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,驅動爐居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,通道封鎖？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,洛薩！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看這架勢　或許自爆裝置已被啟動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看來柯瓦特羅決心放棄這處據點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快讓她停下　否則你也會被捲進去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她的體內寄宿著我的複製品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡的我已不再有價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,防衛機構　全面展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,預備引擎　啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,自動修復開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼　沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.91,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「廣域搜索　成功」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.91,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wide Area Search successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:31.08,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「座標鎖定　距離已測算」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:31.08,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coordinates are specific. Distance calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,區域搜索？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,難道她一直在尋找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可…　可這裡是最深部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人能夠到達這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,貫壁攻擊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太愚蠢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:08.07,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「確認通道安全　解除武裝保險」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:08.07,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Clearance confirmation. Firing lock is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,星煌3級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}天神烈破
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,博士的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,機巧傀儡　完全停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其他地點也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,六課成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奈葉…　媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來　快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐已不能再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:42.79,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「驅動爐破損　管制者缺失　聖王陛下喪失戰意」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.54,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}　Wir wurden beschädigt.　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}Niemand hat die Kontrollposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.79,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heiliger Kaiser verliert Kampfwille.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.71,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「切換為自動防衛模式」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.71,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ab jetzt gehen wir in die Automatikverteidigungssituation ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.59,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「艦載機　全機出動」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.59,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jagdflieger, aufbieten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.01,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「排除艦內的一切異物」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.01,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}　Alle Fremdkörper wegbekommen!　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,做好準備　琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們拚出血路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐　我這就來救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法使自己停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別說洩氣話！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再接近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經明白　自己是古代人的複製品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,奈葉與菲特都並非真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我僅僅是啟動這艘船的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,僅僅是守護王座的生體兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從一開始　我便沒有真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在尋找能保護我\N\N讓我收集魔法知識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是事實！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的悲傷與痛苦\N\N全部都是虛偽的創造品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不該誕生於這個世界的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管誕生方式與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但在我面前哭泣的薇薇歐\N\N絕非虛偽的創造品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡撒嬌哭鼻子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,摔倒後無法自己站起也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不愛吃青椒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,當我難過時懂得安慰我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是我心愛的薇薇歐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管我並非薇薇歐真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但一定會努力成為真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以　不要說自己是不該誕生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正的心情告訴媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我…　我也很愛奈葉媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想永遠與媽媽在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我會救妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,無論何時！　無論何地！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}Restrict Lock{\fs22}\N\N{\fs71}禁錮枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐　可以稍微忍受一下疼痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要擊穿防禦　全力施加魔力打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,能行吧　旭日之心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.57,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「沒問題」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.57,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Clear to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,全力全開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\t(\bord6\3c&H88000BB&)}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,烈動──
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,──聚射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要自己站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應過妳　將成為勇敢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,巨舟　船速低下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上升速度　明顯下降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來　艦隊便可率先抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,7分鐘的時間差被填補了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:07.07,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「聖王陛下失聯　系統崩潰」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:07.07,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heiliger Kaiser keine Reaktion.\NFunktionsverlust des Systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,疾風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:16.58,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「解除艦內全部魔力結合　用於自動修復」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.78,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}　Alle magische Verbindung wird abgehängt,　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.58,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fsp-12}Fü{\fsp0}r die Regeneration des Kronschiffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.55,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs71}「請全體乘員進入休眠模式」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.55,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Alle Mann am Ort, Minifunktion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我所知的全部真相　都保存在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我會保管好它的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,能替我照顧好埃基特與露緹茜婭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這些不幸的孩子\N\N都是因為未能邂逅本該邂逅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,埃基特　與妳和露緹茜婭共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是一段不錯的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好湛藍的天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我與雷吉亞斯曾發誓守護的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳們堅守信念　以我們為鑒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂婭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,各地的機巧傀儡已停止活動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是奈葉她們成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,昴　銀河沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,巨舟的上升已被阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但內部的戰鬥仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們與內部的奈葉她們失去了聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,室內的撤退支援與救助任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是陸戰士的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,銀姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把它帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,奈葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,當事件迎來終息的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,當機動六課結束使命的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.75,0:25:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即使相互分離
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.41,0:25:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也會有永不消失的寶物　永不忘卻的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.21,0:25:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,下集　魔法少女奈葉StrikerS　最終話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.80,0:25:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,未來的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.55,0:25:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,起飛！
